                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17950114-43-defend378 t17950114-43-punish258"></join>
               
                  </rs> (Aged 19.)</p>
               <p>Judgment respited.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Mr. Justice HEATH.</p>
